summary: This document contains location data related to a mobile number associated with an investigation. It details the confidence level of the location estimate and the data source used for the tracking. The document emphasizes caution in using the location data for investigative purposes due to potential inaccuracies.
keyFacts: The document is a location tracking report initiated on June 30, 2020.
The mobile number's location was estimated with a confidence level of 90.
The location data is sourced from AT&T's 4G-GMPC system.
The radius of the location estimate is 1410 meters.
The document warns about the potential inaccuracies of the location data.
